    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Calling out a word of power, you invigorate your target's spirit and bolster their life energy.</em></p><p><strong>Healing</strong></p><p>This spell has no effect on &amp;reference[construct].</p><ul><li><p>Target gains hit points equal to [[/healing 1d4 + @attributes.spellmod]]{1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier} .</p><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>*Upcasting</strong>: Increase healing by [[/healing 1d4]]{1d4} for each spell level above 1st.</p></div></div></div></div>",
